<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Open a table in the data editor</b></p><p>When you double-click a table in the <span class="control">Database</span> tool window (<span class="shortcut">View | Tool Windows | Database</span>), the table opens in the data editor.</p><p>In the data editor, you can create and delete new entries, modify existing ones, filter data by a column, view data in the separate viewer, and compare two tables.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/db_pl_tips_DBTableEditor.png" alt="Data editor of a table" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>